snippet: The Big Ten female athlete of the year award no longer is named for Suzy Favor Hamilton, the conference said.
abstract: Big Ten female athlete of the year award is no longer named for Suzy Favor Hamilton, Olympic track star from Wisconsin who acknowledged that she had worked as a prostitute; Amanda Kessel, a Minnesota hockey player, is named the winner of the award,
lead_paragraph: The Big Ten female athlete of the year award no longer is named for Suzy Favor Hamilton, the conference said.

headline.main: Favor Hamilton’s Name Is Off Big Ten Award
